    CDRIVER-1156: Organize our defines a bit better
    
    MONGOC_ENABLE_SSL[_OPENSSL|_SECURE_CHANNEL|_SECURE_TRANSPORT]
    MONGOC_ENABLE_CRYPTO[_LIBCRYPTO|_CNG|_COMMON_CRYPTO]

