commit a5c799aced1bc5defd99d3e8284d4ecfa42ac33e
Author: A. Jesse Jiryu Davis <jesse@mongodb.com>
Date:   Sun Aug 16 09:08:41 2015 -0400

    leak formatting "too large" err message
    
    Introduced with CDRIVER-654.

