Author: A. Jesse Jiryu Davis <jesse@mongodb.com>
Date:   Sun Jun 21 01:04:44 2015 -0400

    1.1.8 Release
    
    Signed-off-by: A. Jesse Jiryu Davis <jesse@mongodb.com>

 CMakeLists.txt                |  4 ++--
 NEWS                          | 18 ++++++++++++++++++
 README.rst                    | 12 ++++++------
